data.title: Gmail - International Investment Law (Quiz Test-1)
data.meta_description: Gmail - International Investment Law (Quiz Test-1) - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document is a notification from Google Forms about a quiz on International Investment Law that was completed by a student named Amit Baydwal with roll number 015 from the National Law University Odisha. The quiz contained 27 multiple choice questions related to key concepts and cases in international investment law.
